<element name="Drain Life" type="Spell" source="Spencer's Homebrew" id="ID_PHB_SPELL_DRAIN_LIFE">
<supports>Sorcerer, Wizard, Warlock</supports>
<description>
<p>You point your finger to a creature to siphon its life force. Make a ranged spell attack against the target. On a hit, target takes 1d6 necrotic damage, and you regain hit points equal to half the amount of necrotic damage dealt.</p>
<p class="indent">The spell's damage increases by 1d6 at 5th level (2d6), 11th level (3d6), and 17th level (4d6).</p>
</description>
